Hetuduka, Tika
Hetuduka, Saṃkiliṭṭhattika
Asaṃkiliṭṭhaasaṃkilesikapada
Pañhāvāra
Paccanīyuddhāra
208.
389Hetu asaṃkiliṭṭhaasaṃkilesiko dhammo hetussa asaṃkiliṭṭhaasaṃkilesikassa dhammassa sahajātapaccayena paccayo…  upanissayapaccayena paccayo. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
209.
390Nahetuyā nava naārammaṇe nava. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
391Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe tīṇi. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
392Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe tīṇi. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
393(Yathā kusalattike pañhāvārassa anulomampi paccanīyampi anulomapaccanīyampi paccanīyānulomampi gaṇitaṃ, evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)
394Hetudukasaṃkiliṭṭhattikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.
